{"id":232822654,"title":"超簡單✨棉花糖布丁🍮","content":"烤肉節(?)時在全聯買了兩包棉花糖在宿舍嗑\n結果就這樣吃到要期末了還吃不完😂\n就去找找棉花糖能做什麼花樣\n現在就來跟大家分享~\n\n材料只需要棉花糖x1&牛奶x2\nhttps://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzD.jpg\n因為我棉花糖是吃剩大概一半多，所以牛奶倒了約一瓶半\n可以斟酌兩種的量\n\n做法：\n牛奶跟棉花糖+在一起\n然後進微波把它融化\n(可以先把棉花糖切小塊比較好融化)\n\n融化完後先稍微放涼\n然後再用濾網把它過濾到容器裡\n之後放進冰箱冰到隔天\n就會得到\n↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓↓\n\n\n\n將將✨\nhttps://i.imgur.com/ClIw6Fo.jpg\n很輕鬆就可以做出來的甜點❤\n吃起來很像奶酪~\n\n大家沒事也來trytry看吧~~~","excerpt":"烤肉節（？）時在全聯買了兩包棉花糖在宿舍嗑，結果就這樣吃到要期末了還吃不完，就去找找棉花糖能做什麼花樣，現在就來跟大家分享~，材料只需要棉花糖x1&牛奶x2，因為我棉花糖是吃剩大概一半多，所以牛奶倒了","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-04T06:13:26.629Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T06:15:56.283Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":219,"tags":[],"topics":["懶人料理","懶人甜點","奶酪","棉花糖布丁"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"輔仁大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":219}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzD.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/ClIw6Fo.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9963f086-68f9-4c9a-bf43-86fa5d697c51","url":"https://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzDl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzDl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzDl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-04T06:13:26.629Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T06:15:56.283Z"},{"id":"9963f086-68f9-4c9a-bf43-86fa5d697c51","url":"https://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzD.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/VeAfUzD","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/VeAfUzDl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-04T06:13:26.629Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T06:15:56.283Z"},{"id":"acf05e63-77f5-4fb